text: Miloud M'Sellek (born 1937) is a Moroccan gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:Living people Category:Moroccan male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Morocco Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Casablanca
